title: Twilight-Audio Book CD Ripped
description:
Here it is finally. I have the actual version from the CDs. 

I tried my best to make a decent version of the Audio Book from a download as one large file.

But Now ... I got the real deal going. 

Enjoy this. I upoloaded the other version very similar to this one, and I will say, DO NOT BOTHER TO DOWNLOAD IT ANYMORE!

It's quite alright. This one is better now.

Please Seed ....

I believe it is 160 KBPS but I cant rememeber. Don't hold it against me.

Very well organized like all of my Audio Books. 

Also if you like Harry Potter I put all seven of them up very good quality and organized.
